It's psychological game like Caligula forcing people to salute his horse and torturing them to death if they refused. Similarly we have a smiling blonde lady with a Barbie Doll universe name. "Pam Blondie". It's obvious a person like this can never be a real player in politics.

"Pam Bondi" is the MAGA-fied version of what Thomas777 said about Hillary Clinton being like Caligula's horse. When America terror bombs some Balkan country then sends Hillary or some other clown in to "negotiate", it confuses the normal groups of people there and gaslights them.

It's similar to what Galkovsky said about Leni Riefenstahl being not so much a film director, but an actress playing a director with a team of hundreds of people taking footage, editing films, etc. while she drinks champagne with some ministers. A pretty face of a huge machine.
